# Articles: Layout, Spacing, Images

## Canonical structure
- One outer `<article className="pt-24 pb-16">` wrapper for the page.
- One **article body wrapper** with `prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none`.
- Avoid nested `prose` wrappers unless there is a strong reason.

## Canonical article body spacing
Use descendant selectors so nested content gets spacing:
- Paragraphs: `[&_p]:mb-6 [&_p:last-child]:mb-0`
- Blockquotes: `[&_blockquote]:my-8 [&_blockquote:last-child]:mb-0`
- Lists: `[&_ul]:my-6 [&_ol]:my-6 [&_li]:my-2` + explicit `list-*` + `pl-*`

## Hero images
- Put hero images in `client/public/images/articles/`.
- Use descriptive `alt` text.
- Add the same hero path to the article card entry in `client/src/pages/Articles.tsx`.

## Cache-busting guideline
If an updated image doesn’t appear in production:
- Prefer renaming the file (`*-v2.png`) and updating references rather than trying to “force refresh”.

